fields.name: laptop_1
fields.description: Budget (office) laptop. The model does not have high power or high screen quality, but they are enough for web surfing and work in office programs.

fields.name: laptop_2
fields.description: Versatile laptop for home and office use. The device is capable of performing most of all kinds of tasks, including working in heavy programs, editing photos and videos, and playing modern online games. It has high reliability and good build quality.

fields.name: laptop_3
fields.description: A professional laptop aimed at the business sector, so it has a thin metal case, high autonomy and performance.

fields.name: laptop_4
fields.description: Gaming laptop. Everything in this model is aimed at high gaming performance, and the dimensions and design come to the fore. These are powerful laptops with a noisy cooling system and an aggressive gaming design.

fields.name: smartphone_1
fields.description: The smartphone is included in the budget price segment. It has a quality build quality and modern design.

fields.name: smartphone_2
fields.description: The smartphone has high performance, large memory capacity and good shooting quality both in the daytime and at night.
